#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kwordquiz.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KWordQuiz is a general purpose flash card program. It can be used for "
"vocabulary learning and many other subjects. It provides an editor and five "
"different flashcard quiz modes. It uses the KVTML file format and "
"contributed files can be downloaded from within the application."
msgstr ""
"KWordQuiz es un programam de carta  mnemonica (flsh card) de proposito "
"general. Il pote esser  usate per apprender vocabularioe multe altere "
"subjectos. Il forni un editor e cinque modos differente de quiz de "
"flashcard. Il usa le formato KVTML e file contribuite pote esser discargate "
"ab intra le application."

